tiers.ability_description: Whenever Dark Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.

The first time each Hutt Cartel ally falls below 50% Health, they gain Damage Immunity for 1 turn, which can't be copied, dispelled, or prevented.\n\nWhenever an enemy takes damage from a Thermal Detonator expiring, Hutt Cartel allies recover 5% Health and Protection, gain 5% Turn Meter, and there is a 50% chance that enemy is inflicted with a Thermal Detonator for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled, prevented, or resisted.

The max cooldown of Inventive is reduced by 1. Whenever Boushh inflicts Thermal Detonators on an enemy, inflict an additional Thermal Detonator for 2 turns and Hutt Cartel allies gain 10% Armor Penetration (max 70%) and 10% Turn Meter (once per turn).
